note: merged or not i think that the original `epoch++` should be limited to `MAX_SAFE_INTEGER`

The only downside is the limitation of bitwise operators to 32 bits. This, of course, could be overcome if we want to use all the 53 bits of `MAX_SAFE_INTEGER` with `Math.pow(2,n)` but i'm sure that it would be less efficient.

